{"tid":1894632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孔聖堂中學校董會聲明","createTime":"2020-02-24T05:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T06:34:54.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17a7bcc38d52fc5fb8b22dca06b7e8e74bfea08e","tid":1894632,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2584687148519841&amp;id=1484748651847035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2584687148519841%26id%3D1484748651847035&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=bfe0b030\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2584687148519841&amp;id=1484748651847035</a><br />\n<br />\n就有關署理副校長何栢欣老師近日在網上針對警方貼文一事，本校董會作出以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n1. 何副校長是以個人名義在其個人Facebook專頁發表該文。該文章與本校無關，而該篇貼文發表事前未曾知會本校，或尋求本校的許可，屬於其個人行為。<br />\n<br />\n2. 孔聖堂中學及其校董會一直堅守政治不進校門原則，反對暴力及任何違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n3. 本校董會已成立了專責調查小組，務求查明該事件的來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n4. 於2月24日起，何副校長將暫時停職，直至調查小組完成報告。"},{"pid":"674eb3c6c09f5319f02cd8c3999f1605d440fd0d","tid":1894632,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"又話個人行為<br />\n又話政治不進校園<br />\n但係就停人職<br />\n精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525ddba813ab2af52472a95ba8cfe4a60f7bd992","tid":1894632,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f298927564e44b4961b59297f61000d00f94d5b0","tid":1894632,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T06:34:54.000Z","msg":"應該立即起底班校董"}]}